;yes&quot;elseecho &quot;no&quot;fi 字符串判断： 1234-z &quot;$XXX&quot; #XXX是否为空-n &quot;$XXX&quot; #XXX是否非空&quot;a&quot; == &quot;b&quot; #a与b是否一致&quot;a&quot; != &quot;b&quot; #a与b是否不一致 示例： 12345678#!/bin/bashname=&quot;a&quot;if [[ -z &quot;$name&quot; ]]; thenecho &quot;null&quot;elseecho &quot;not null&quot;fi 在使用双方括号时，引用变量name时可以不加引号或使用单引号","categories":[{"name":"Knowledge","slug":"Knowledge","permalink":"http://example.com/categories/Knowledge/"}],"tags":[]},{"title":"helloworld","slug":"helloworld","date":"2024-02-22T05:46:12.000Z","updated":"2024-02-22T07:24:25.206Z","comments":true,"path":"2024/02/21/helloworld/","permalink":"http://example.com/2024/02/21/helloworld/","excerpt":"","text":"hi~","categories":[{"name":"Knowledge","slug":"Knowledge","permalink":"http://example.com/categories/Knowledge/"}],"tags":[{"name":"test","slug":"test","permalink":"http://example.com/tags/test/"}]}],"categories":[{"name":"Knowledge","slug":"Knowledge","permalink":"http://example.com/categories/Knowledge/"}],"tags":[{"name":"hexo","slug":"hexo","permalink":"http://example.com/tags/hexo/"},{"name":"test","slug":"test","permalink":"http://example.com/tags/test/"}]}